data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled on a sprawling 25-acre estate. Whether you're a nature enthusiast, a family looking for the perfect home, or an investor seeking a rare gem, 5702 Buchanan Loop Road has it all.  Property Highlights: **Bedrooms: 5 generously sized bedrooms for ultimate comfort. **Bathrooms: 4 full bathrooms and 2 half bathrooms **Office Space: Perfect for remote work or a home-based business. **Key Property Highlights: 2 water heaters and HVAC system, less than two years old; A fully insulated and climate controlled garage to keep your vehicles and hobbies protected from the elements; A 2-story barn, installed in 2017, for your storage, workshop, or equestrian needs and new roof installed in 2021.   This property offers the best of both worlds – the serenity of a countryside retreat with the convenience of being just a short drive away from local shopping.
